@startuml data-flow
title Flux de date - de la senzor la baza de date

skinparam ArrowColor #555555
skinparam ObjectBackgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam ObjectBorderColor #999999
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FFFDE7

' ============================================================
' ETAPE TRANSFORMARE
' ============================================================

object "SensorFrame\n(firmware, binar BLE)" as F1 #FFECB3 {
  version       : uint8
  seqNumber     : uint32
  timestampMs   : uint32 (ms de la boot)
  heartRateBpm  : uint16
  spO2Percent   : uint8
  humidityX10   : uint16
  tempCX10      : int16
  ecgSamples    : uint16[0..80]
  flags         : uint8
}

object "SensorSample\n(obiect Android)" as F2 #E1F5FE {
  timestamp   : Instant (UTC)
  ecgBytes    : byte[]
  umiditate   : BigDecimal
  temperatura : BigDecimal
  puls        : Integer
}

object "UplinkBatch\n(JSON uplink HTTP)" as F3 #C8E6C9 {
  batchId      : UUID (idempotency key)
  patientId    : UUID
  deviceId     : String
  windowStart  : Instant
  windowEnd    : Instant
  series       : MeasurementSeries
  accelBurst   : AccelerometerBurst
}

object "MeasurementBatch\n(entitate SQL)" as F4 #F3E5F5 {
  id           : UUID
  patientId    : UUID (FK)
  receivedAt   : Instant
  windowStart  : Instant
  windowEnd    : Instant
  samplesJson  : NVARCHAR(max) (blob JSON)
}

object "AlertEvent\n(flux paralel)" as A1 #FFCDD2 {
  id           : UUID
  patientId    : UUID
  ruleId       : UUID
  triggeredAt  : Instant
  measuredValue: Number
  severity     : Enum
  message      : String
}

' ============================================================
' TRANZITII
' ============================================================

F1 -right-> F2 : parseSensorFrame()\n(LITTLE_ENDIAN,\nclock corectat\nla timpul telefonului)

F2 -right-> F3 : aggregateWindow(30 s)\n- mediere puls/temp/umid\n- pastrare ECG reprezentativ\n- atasare burst accel (~30 esantioane)\n- generare batchId = UUID

F3 -right-> F4 : POST /ingestion/measurements\n- verif idempotenta batchId\n- validare range (temp, puls)\n- INSERT in Azure SQL

F2 .down.> A1 : AlarmEvaluatorService\n(daca depaseste\nNormalRangeProfile)
A1 -down-> F4 : POST /ingestion/alerts\n(flux asincron,\nNOT blocheaza batch-ul)

note bottom of F1
  Produs de ESP32
  la ~10 s / fereastra
end note

note bottom of F2
  Produs in Android
  dupa parseSensorFrame.
  Trecut prin SensorAggregatorService
  si AlarmEvaluatorService.
end note

note bottom of F3
  Produs in Android de
  CloudSyncService dupa
  ~30 s (3 ferestre de 10 s).
  Trimis HTTPS + JWT.
end note

note bottom of F4
  Persistat in Azure SQL
  prin IngestionService.
  MonitoringService citeste
  pentru grafice / rapoarte.
end note

@enduml
